.RE
.RS  "*" 2 "Static Power, IRdrop and EM Analysis" in the Voltus IC Power Integrity Solution User Guide  "*" 2 "Dynamic Power and IRDrop Analysis" in the Voltus IC Power Integrity Solution User Guide
.RE
.P
